cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image synthesis and utilizes deep learning techniques for the same. 
2. cs.GR (Graphics) is also a likely category as the paper focuses on generating photo-realistic indoor scene renderings for design applications. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel model based on a structure-appearance joint embedding learned from both images and wireframes. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper utilizes deep learning techniques for the proposed model. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with generating indoor scene renderings that can be used in multimedia applications.
